{"tid":237570,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"［少甜］我收到atv 百萬富翁邀請信 參加節目","createTime":"2017-05-10T12:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T06:14:56.000Z","uid":112303,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"896c62e80e2917894b709f59fed34f881ac3e54a","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:48:32.000Z","msg":"手機響鈴來留名～<br />\n<br />\n「喂」<br />\n<br />\n一個+86字頭嘅電話號碼打黎<br />\n<br />\n「你呀婆急病入左醫院呀！」<br />\n<br />\n騙徒手法層出不窮，將「個仔」換左「呀婆」<br />\n<br />\n差啲令聰明絕頂嘅我墜入圈套<br />\n<br />\n但作為一個超級電視迷，睇過無數次廣告，點會發現唔到<br />\n<br />\n依個係一個陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n「嗰到咪有電話亭囉！」<br />\n<br />\n既然騙徒手法都不停轉變，我點可以一成不變<br />\n<br />\n反正都係用黎擊退騙徒，用邊句都一樣啦<br />\n<br />\n「仆街仔，玩玩玩！我係你老母呀！ 生舊燒肉好過生你個on9仔」<br />\n<br />\n咦， 依個騙徒有料到喎 。 咁經典嘅句子 都可以改頭換面<br />\n<br />\n應該係資深玩家。<br />\n<br />\n正當我諗緊點擊退佢嗰陣<br />\n<br />\n「我依加翻左鄉下睇住啊婆， 屋企枱頭有3000蚊<br />\n  依2個禮拜你自己搞掂啦！ 仲有仲有 ，atv 寄左封信俾你 係咁啦！翻黎先教訓你個仆街仔」<br />\n<br />\n嘟..嘟..嘟..嘟..<br />\n<br />\n哼， 不攻自破。我都仲未出招！<br />\n<br />\n遇上我真係唔好彩，我諗佢都知呃我唔到，<br />\n<br />\n所以廢事浪費時間，搵下個目標。算你醒目！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n翻屋企途中，諗深一層 ，直接cut 佢線咪得囉<br />\n<br />\n睇黎下次可以用依招，邊個騙徒都奈我唔何！<br />\n<br />\n哇哈哈哈哈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我扭開屋企大門入屋，咦咁黑嘅，屌！！個仆街老母<br />\n<br />\n又去左打麻雀又唔早啲出聲 ， 又要落多次去買飯食。<br />\n<br />\n唉，等我放低書包先。 咦....3000...蚊...?<br />\n<br />\nEr ...依獲我仲唔冚家產？"},{"pid":"0dc5f2010451e0af540517f78f252295d84de116","tid":237570,"uid":12435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"413317df05bc2ca3b6f46228342781fbd5b0ff01","tid":237570,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T12:53:48.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b75acba2dae3dbdc0abc4707a82f1e01915a1455","tid":237570,"uid":13719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T13:35:20.000Z","msg":"啪定手先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1fb92edabd7e7e0bd698f25deed6f89a1e929f","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:27:09.000Z","msg":"之後我落街買頹m外賣，自從無左板雞之後<br />\n<br />\n脆弱雞腿包餐就係我必食之選<br />\n<br />\n翻到屋企第一件事做咩？<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味 緊係剝哂衫褲剝哂鞋 wooo 之後尻叫啦<br />\n<br />\n難得兩個星期無皇管，一定要玩盡佢，乜撚都唔理喇<br />\n<br />\n搵啲野搞下先<br />\n<br />\n我快快手手食完個頹m，沖個涼之後<br />\n<br />\n係我個書包攞出一疊past paper 埋頭苦幹咁做<br />\n<br />\n今年dse , 實行chur 到盡！<br />\n<br />\n正常我諗緊cos 係鄰邊除斜邊 定係 底乘高除2 之際<br />\n<br />\n「atv寄左封信俾你呀」依句說話係我腦海出現<br />\n<br />\n下？亞視唔係執柒左喇咩！？<br />\n<br />\n我立即去飯枱摷下封信<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恭喜！ 你已補選中參加百萬富翁 問答比賽<br />\n<br />\n請於2017年5月12號到亞洲電視參與錄影<br />\n<br />\n節目勝出者會獲得100萬獎金<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n噢。。。100萬。。贏左都無錢比啦<br />\n<br />\n唔通亞視要捲土重來？ 秘密搞當年最收得嘅百萬富翁？<br />\n<br />\n捲土重來即係有資金啦 即係唔會拖錢啦<br />\n<br />\n以我才智 100萬？無難道！ 我仲有drama 底<br />\n<br />\n問咩莎士比亞嗰啲問題一定輕鬆答。<br />\n<br />\n而且我又無fd 又無女 2個禮拜咁多<br />\n<br />\n去玩下都好！<br />\n<br />\n於是，我決定5月12號 單刀赴會。<br />\n<br />\n參加百萬富翁！<br />\n<br />\n____________________________________<br />\n<br />\n巴打們好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  小弟唔係寫開故<br />\n<br />\n文筆又差 中文作文得lv2 標點更加唔洗講<br />\n<br />\n不過突然想寫個故,寫下平時ff啲野<br />\n<br />\n大家可以當日記咁睇 <br />\n<br />\n無聊無野做就睇下<br />\n<br />\n我係諗到乜就寫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多多包涵"},{"pid":"1a2b4bfafca5a86dba6fde1c5bda28ebf389511a","tid":237570,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:29:17.000Z","msg":"唔通係去亞視同金鈴啪啪啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c04ad542533966991f569106c21031217a6bb4","tid":237570,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"期待 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a47b32e41457f9bf56e6e53361637225b1f3c0","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:35:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔通係去亞視同金鈴啪啪啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n曾俊華口味有啲重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d847ff21109cbcfc2f2f649e04048320912da934","tid":237570,"uid":3688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:35:33.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38369959b21159c3e1e78b55459ce56e15aad136","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T14:42:13.000Z","msg":"反正都係諗到乜就寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一夠多人就去甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cb5c7e26f7571a399ae6fb5e4e239cc73ee6b4","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"為左預備12號嘅比賽<br />\n<br />\n我首先睇左次激戰，了解下比賽選手嘅心理質素<br />\n<br />\n我整合左幾點<br />\n1.冷靜<br />\n2.保持節奏<br />\n3.必要時甩較<br />\n<br />\n之後再睇左幾本10萬個為什麼<br />\n<br />\n今舖仲唔萬無一失？一百萬 袋袋平安呀<br />\n<br />\n11號當晚<br />\n<br />\n我打開Facebook <br />\n<br />\nSearch 小藍<br />\n<br />\n唔...泳衣照<br />\n<br />\n噢<br />\n<br />\n噢<br />\n<br />\n呼....<br />\n<br />\n呀....<br />\n<br />\n射左。<br />\n<br />\n小藍係我地班嘅女神<br />\n<br />\n7 3分界 眼大大<br />\n<br />\n白白淨 細細粒<br />\n<br />\n乳出半驚人 仲要係a0<br />\n<br />\n非常適合做我女朋友<br />\n<br />\n所以 <br />\n<br />\n我由中一起 已經係佢隻兵<br />\n<br />\n幫佢買飯 做功課<br />\n<br />\n裝windows 搞破解<br />\n<br />\n為左佢上刀山落油獲 在所不惜<br />\n<br />\n努力過後 係有回報的<br />\n<br />\n中4嗰年 我終於可以同佢坐<br />\n<br />\n佢只係 摺 左一聲 我個心即刻甜哂<br />\n<br />\n睇黎我同佢嘅關係 又進一大步<br />\n<br />\n回過神 已經係晚上十點半<br />\n<br />\n早啲睡先 迎接聽日嘅比賽！"},{"pid":"f8215906344b66f4785c52e5588c4b18b5c0acf1","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:13:09.000Z","msg":"其實我寫啲野係咪咁悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  定係你地得個睇字<br />\n<br />\n小弟鐘意熱鬧啲 就算黎黎去去都係嗰幾個人傾<br />\n<br />\n都好"},{"pid":"1dcfc331e31466ac55ac026da37b0b1f9b52c91e","tid":237570,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我寫啲野係咪咁悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  定係你地得個睇字<br />\n<br />\n小弟鐘意熱鬧啲 就算黎黎去去都係嗰幾個人傾<br />\n<br />\n都好</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你岩岩先開始咋喎"},{"pid":"70c56da114985eb1e83d552ef9df4acc95664540","tid":237570,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:21:50.000Z","msg":"你可以出快d"},{"pid":"b6138e3485cc766a9c32596c9b16304f7d2ddb76","tid":237570,"uid":52961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T15:47:09.000Z","msg":"幾有新意<br />\n樓主 有觀眾架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打電話記得打比我答問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79e3325cc7edc9a26c2a6f5f774cd89419763ab","tid":237570,"uid":12435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T16:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c5fddc66df9bbacffcb1438e5fc68caaa332c4","tid":237570,"uid":6970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:15:05.000Z","msg":"比個正評你啦 見topic幾得意就入左嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c1b729426296b88b2309f7b4524281bbabcbbab","tid":237570,"uid":17394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:17:57.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"0bec9ce48850571ae384e33d8fc4f7bffd3d7fca","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:24:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實我寫啲野係咪咁悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  定係你地得個睇字<br />\n<br />\n小弟鐘意熱鬧啲 就算黎黎去去都係嗰幾個人傾<br />\n<br />\n都好</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你岩岩先開始咋喎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> r下水吹姐 無人都照打"},{"pid":"30052fac7c08407ba3816fbd352374c03ab737b8","tid":237570,"uid":20008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:25:53.000Z","msg":"快啦屌"},{"pid":"ad0827ce532af4cc31e14536ee737efc46f5b78f","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:26:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你可以出快d</blockquote><br />\n我都係得閒先打下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔預你地當其他估咁追 <br />\n有時記得嘅就翻下黎睇"},{"pid":"6cfcec47c3428ce73cece1fb672f3a564ba79bdd","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾有新意<br />\n樓主 有觀眾架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打電話記得打比我答問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係我ff之中 依個唔算有新意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實個目的都係為寫甜"},{"pid":"1ee8e58449c21a56e668dc93124d108cf80ea172","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:28:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快啦屌</blockquote><br />\n見你咁想追 為左你 即刻上床瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8aec618532917ca3599dcc3fbaa9931dc1f467d","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:43:46.000Z","msg":"12號當日 我7點鐘起左身<br />\n<br />\n錄影時間係1930 即係仲有12個鐘預備<br />\n<br />\n我洗個面沖個涼 落樓下發記食個早餐<br />\n<br />\n之後翻上屋企重溫一次 10萬個為什麼<br />\n<br />\n然後落街跑步 俾個頭腦清晰一翻 <br />\n<br />\n準備迎接100萬翻屋企<br />\n<br />\n跑跑下 我撞到一個人<br />\n<br />\n無錯， 我諗大家都估到<br />\n<br />\n佢唔係小藍<br />\n<br />\n佢叫呀俊 <br />\n<br />\n俊？邊撚到俊呀？睇過<br />\n<br />\n又真係幾俊<br />\n<br />\n呀俊係我地班嘅一個男仔<br />\n<br />\n幾靚仔，但叫佢男神又唔算<br />\n<br />\n始終讀書 運動樣樣唔精<br />\n<br />\n不過...小藍成日癡住佢<br />\n<br />\n有次無意中得知 小藍成日上佢屋企做功課<br />\n<br />\n好彩 做功課姐 純潔嘅小藍依舊純潔<br />\n<br />\n我同呀俊點左個頭就各散東西<br />\n<br />\n畢竟，我地都唔熟<br />\n<br />\n之後1800我就出發去亞視了。<br />\n<br />\n係巴士到 望住小藍張相<br />\n<br />\n係到諗 ，贏左100萬之後 可以點貢獻俾佢<br />\n<br />\n萬萬都估唔到 ....依次係我最後一次望住小藍嘅樣。"},{"pid":"5cf02ba89059aca5bc0af6b97dd066b921cf935c","tid":237570,"uid":97486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T17:44:02.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"e78904e7e2f09966bbafa660d3a6ae7ce72839db","tid":237570,"uid":101843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T19:08:05.000Z","msg":"支持良心電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"348870636ee67c5a10fe2a5f0996737fa0f3537d","tid":237570,"uid":68988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T19:35:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持良心電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ccf1b7b61daf2242f1b12fd476ac43f4739d2fd","tid":237570,"uid":11070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T20:08:57.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"b04f853d01e709d86ee8a1b7ff88864e58fdbf16","tid":237570,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7eeeb96ddbc01f1b9da6ad28afb4789cc25ffa0","tid":237570,"uid":41803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T23:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb375887ee115e9aa085149b501b9f89eb562b40","tid":237570,"uid":13719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T01:50:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f695c47cd3e39f338f5c6ed5c5e1df6d8e159129","tid":237570,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T03:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664c5e24135d8aeee02404485bc42e09dccea071","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:24:01.000Z","msg":"為左留俾對方一個好印象 我決定搭的士去西貢<br />\n<br />\n落車之後 我自信地走向大門<br />\n<br />\n咦？無保安 咁點入呀<br />\n<br />\n㩒門鐘都無人應機<br />\n<br />\n執左姐 點都有保安呱<br />\n<br />\n係依個時候 我有2個諗法<br />\n<br />\n1.既然都無人， 不如爬入去探下險<br />\n<br />\n2.掉頭翻屋企瞓教 浪費左幾十蚊車錢<br />\n<br />\n其實膽小如鼠嘅我 根本唔洗考慮乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n入到去之後， 人有三急<br />\n<br />\n搵下廁所先<br />\n<br />\n沿途陰風陣陣 雖然日光日白<br />\n<br />\n但係都感受到 孤獨嘅怨氣<br />\n<br />\n可能已經太耐無人睇了<br />\n<br />\n噢 搵到廁所喇<br />\n<br />\n作為一個男人，我決定入女廁屙<br />\n<br />\n咁大個仔都未入過女廁<br />\n<br />\n依加大好機會 襯無人<br />\n<br />\n吸收下女人嘅仙氣先<br />\n<br />\n分分鐘 暗星小花係到屙過屎<br />\n<br />\n諗到依到 我條巨龍不奇然扯左半旗<br />\n<br />\n只需要8秒 我就可以從草叢中找出樹幹<br />\n<br />\n心裏不禁讚嘆母親嘅優良基因<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呯！ <br />\n<br />\n廁格門呯埋左！<br />\n<br />\n仆街<br />\n<br />\n反鎖？<br />\n<br />\n邊個玩野？<br />\n<br />\n個cam 係邊到？<br />\n<br />\n真人show?<br />\n<br />\n正當我想爬出去嗰陣<br />\n<br />\n發現自己手腳無力<br />\n<br />\n視線愈黎愈濛糊...<br />\n<br />\n我...頂唔順喇<br />\n<br />\n坐左係小花用過嘅廁板上<br />\n<br />\n一路loop收花嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n多謝 但我唔要 我睡著了"},{"pid":"30e4d4d14fb8787de3e5f2a5e281a0d0269392ad","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <del>為左留俾對方一個好印象 我決定搭的士去西貢<br />\n<br />\n落車之後 我自信地走向大門</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咦？無保安 咁點入呀<br />\n<br />\n㩒門鐘都無人應機<br />\n<br />\n執左姐 點都有保安呱<br />\n<br />\n係依個時候 我有2個諗法<br />\n<br />\n1.既然都無人， 不如爬入去探下險<br />\n<br />\n2.掉頭翻屋企瞓教 浪費左幾十蚊車錢<br />\n<br />\n其實膽小如鼠嘅我 根本唔洗考慮乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n入到去之後， 人有三急<br />\n<br />\n搵下廁所先<br />\n<br />\n沿途陰風陣陣 雖然日光日白<br />\n<br />\n但係都感受到 孤獨嘅怨氣<br />\n<br />\n可能已經太耐無人睇了<br />\n<br />\n噢 搵到廁所喇<br />\n<br />\n作為一個男人，我決定入女廁屙<br />\n<br />\n咁大個仔都未入過女廁<br />\n<br />\n依加大好機會 襯無人<br />\n<br />\n吸收下女人嘅仙氣先<br />\n<br />\n分分鐘 暗星小花係到屙過屎<br />\n<br />\n諗到依到 我條巨龍不奇然扯左半旗<br />\n<br />\n只需要8秒 我就可以從草叢中找出樹幹<br />\n<br />\n心裏不禁讚嘆母親嘅優良基因<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呯！ <br />\n<br />\n廁格門呯埋左！<br />\n<br />\n仆街<br />\n<br />\n反鎖？<br />\n<br />\n邊個玩野？<br />\n<br />\n個cam 係邊到？<br />\n<br />\n真人show?<br />\n<br />\n正當我想爬出去嗰陣<br />\n<br />\n發現自己手腳無力<br />\n<br />\n視線愈黎愈濛糊...<br />\n<br />\n我...頂唔順喇<br />\n<br />\n坐左係小花用過嘅廁板上<br />\n<br />\n一路loop收花嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n多謝 但我唔要 我睡著了</blockquote>"},{"pid":"62d031e7e048ec0e88ee1b89e8368160f784e62a","tid":237570,"uid":22095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T04:31:45.000Z","msg":"正評I'm"},{"pid":"9b2401d5ce2d4e0062f1e377cbfa8efdaa6935f5","tid":237570,"uid":31318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T06:30:49.000Z","msg":"幾搞笑"},{"pid":"bd09408b3c8670db000001da8e340f99e6fe7e4f","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T10:00:02.000Z","msg":"當全世界已為依個係輕鬆小品嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n我已經被矇眼綁住手<br />\n<br />\n綁架？<br />\n<br />\n我屋企無錢架喎 最多一年去一次澳門旅行<br />\n<br />\n點解要係我喎<br />\n<br />\n我幾廿歲人 依啲野唔關我事架！<br />\n<br />\n突然 傳黎一則米奇老鼠聲嘅廣播<br />\n<br />\n「大家好，相信大家已經醒左<br />\n<br />\n如果未醒嘅人算佢地唔好彩」<br />\n<br />\n大家？ 即係唔止我一個啦<br />\n<br />\n我個心當堂靜左陣 有個照應嘛<br />\n<br />\n你以為真係有個照應咁爽皮？<br />\n<br />\n「依到有20間房，每間有2個人，你地隻腳綁埋左一齊<br />\n<br />\n你地為對方鬆綁後 ， 要用房嘅工具殺死對方<br />\n<br />\n你地每人都呑左一條鎖鑰 一條係開房門嘅<br />\n<br />\n一條開腳嘅。 每間房只可以有一個人出黎<br />\n<br />\n如果偷雞嘅， 後果自負。<br />\n<br />\n依個遊戲只有一個人勝出<br />\n<br />\n絕對無 打和！！」<br />\n<br />\n「錄影 開始」<br />\n<br />\n當我仲消化緊岩岩嘅野嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n「哎。 依到係邊到？」<br />\n<br />\n咦...？ 邊到？ 佢岩岩先醒？<br />\n<br />\n抑或...扮緊野..？"},{"pid":"6debe56cd0f60a346a8cd98c342440cb25520e88","tid":237570,"uid":12435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T11:15:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁恐怖"},{"pid":"6a7f1766b5e397ebfaee107a914a9d999abc71de","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T11:35:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁恐怖</blockquote><br />\n個故無類型可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過都想搞笑形式"},{"pid":"9412e23d061dd12243c729bcda4ea897d74e5a2c","tid":237570,"uid":115181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T19:04:51.000Z","msg":"咁都話係搞笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好得人驚"},{"pid":"9b8764a44afb4ea594255e98cc05870d81cf95e1","tid":237570,"uid":62024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T21:01:30.000Z","msg":"嚇死咩"},{"pid":"9ecfcb206e67c1981e5f266226be4d6a597a390e","tid":237570,"uid":43674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T22:16:21.000Z","msg":"好廢"},{"pid":"ebd535afe9822b126d44879132d64fae3a62d997","tid":237570,"uid":60052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T00:06:09.000Z","msg":"甜係邊？ 快"},{"pid":"fb0f0c6fc72b82ae8d9d1a5aa24b08a8c664550d","tid":237570,"uid":106480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T00:33:54.000Z","msg":"暫時都幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f989fa3b21322c1910359e84f7ff503f9fc2446","tid":237570,"uid":52961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:04:14.000Z","msg":"樓主出文未"},{"pid":"0863d384bcab788154211114e7e949fc927ca63a","tid":237570,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:10:57.000Z","msg":"嗯..<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇.."},{"pid":"a884673fedb26ac3f7a96a1ce6f96c7b245f36f8","tid":237570,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"5272640f9e1d3e03432ddbe16fc5a136ec187c1f","tid":237570,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T05:03:18.000Z","msg":"咁少文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa46aceba89a2cd31dd6856a4b3b49b19418bcc2","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:51:27.000Z","msg":"「我地兩個俾人捉左，可能係綁架 ，你...岩岩醒？」<br />\n<br />\n「綁架？！我諗住黎參加百萬富翁咋喎！」<br />\n<br />\n佢無視左我問佢係咪岩岩醒個問題<br />\n<br />\n如果我再問會變得好怪<br />\n<br />\n「不如我地互相鬆綁先 ，你過黎吖」<br />\n<br />\n我叫左佢過黎之後 憑住聲音確定對方位置<br />\n<br />\n「落啲落啲 哎呀」<br />\n<br />\n哎 我條巨龍呀 點解條友咁撚蠢，講極都唔明<br />\n<br />\n「係咪依個扣呀？」佢捉住我條皮帶扣<br />\n<br />\n「屌！依個係...」<br />\n<br />\n話口未完 佢已經除左我條褲<br />\n<br />\n因為我被綁嘅方式係成條繩連住頸 仲要長度岩岩好<br />\n<br />\n我對手根本無郁嘅空間<br />\n<br />\n我fing 最佢都唔得<br />\n<br />\n由於我條褲太窄，所以一除係連底褲都除埋<br />\n<br />\n我終於忍唔住發火<br />\n<br />\n「你條仆街 你無腦架 有無驗過智力架？你除左我條褲呀！」<br />\n<br />\n「下 好..好好..對唔住呀！」<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢歉意真係太大..佢居然120度躹躬..<br />\n<br />\n無錯，佢個鼻係貼住我巨龍...<br />\n<br />\n定口，我已經分唔撚清 總之係拿埋一舊嘅五官<br />\n<br />\n依個姿勢定左10秒， 連空氣都停頓左<br />\n<br />\n由於我太少打飛機 個龜頭太敏感，所以我扯左半碌...<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢發現了 蠢唔哂 佢即刻彈翻起身<br />\n<br />\n繼續鬆綁，太尷尬喇！！！！<br />\n<br />\n所以我決定講野 打開話題<br />\n<br />\n「係呢..」<br />\n<br />\n點知佢打斷左我<br />\n<br />\n「我處黎架！」<br />\n<br />\n。。。。 。。。。。 <br />\n<br />\n屌 我塊面紅撚過蕃茄 一定！<br />\n<br />\n佢究竟係咪真係咁蠢？<br />\n<br />\n「我..我乜野意思都無架！ 你叫咩名呀？」<br />\n<br />\n我再次轉話題<br />\n<br />\n「我叫呀希」<br />\n<br />\n下..呀希？ 你係呀希？哦哦哦...你就係呀希"},{"pid":"b1d8d71df1e5a44b50000b560913a86988a3ff7e","tid":237570,"uid":112303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T09:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主出文未</blockquote><br />\n出了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  依兩日無瞓過 趕pofo"}]}